{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_040.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x22,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x16d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Then, I'll take those two small bags. Also, I'll take all of these rocks that you have."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Okay, thank you for your patronage! Goodness, mister, you're very generous!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x172,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I'm buying them because I need them. There's nothing extraordinary about that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Of course. But the rocks in my shop, people usually only buy one as a souvenir..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "So I'm happy someone like you came by."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x16e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm sure most people have no use for them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Regina and...Mr. Keith! Hello!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x199,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Welcome, Ayesha. You know this customer?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yes. This is my teacher, Mr. Keith!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I clearly denied that before.<CR>Is your memory that poor? "
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "That's right. Oh, but still..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I'm only thinking of you as my teacher in my heart, so that shouldn't cause any problems for you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That's a subtly annoying thought...<CR>Your self-assertiveness is worth<CR>praising, in a way, yet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I have come this far without caring about what others thought of me and my goals, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I guess my credit finally ran out. I truly did reap what I sowed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Umm, by the way, what did you buy?<CR>Stuff you're gonna use for alchemy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I got some good alloys.<CR>This shop has quality items."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, I work hard to dig them up!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "They're very useful. It takes time to get items of this kind, whether you make them or gather them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "He's a regular. He's bought stuff from me a number of times now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I'll be grateful if you can get the same things next time, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "All right, I'll have them all prepared, so please come again!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "...Umm, Mr. Keith, was it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "...My name is Keithgriff. You can just call me Keith from now on."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Oh, please wait!<CR>Regina, I'll see you later!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Are those rocks really that rare?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "They aren't scarce. You can find them in any region."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "They're useful as ingredients for liquid solvents, but commoners don't have much use for them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I see... That's very helpful. I need to write that down when I get home..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "You're very passionate. I remember those days as well, however..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "How long do you intend to follow me? Did you not have business with that shop earlier?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's right! Oops, I totally got sucked in..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I'll be going back. Please teach me more later, Mr. Keith!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Goodness..."
        }
    ]
}